    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="环境"><a href="#环境" class="headerlink" title="环境"></a>环境</h2><ul><li>centos7</li><li>内存2g</li><li>jdk1.8</li><li>zookeeper3.5.5</li><li>说明：参考资料 <a href="https://zookeeper.apache.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">zookeeper官网 </a>  <a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/lsdb/p/7297731.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">努力改个网名</a></li></ul><h2 id="下载-amp-安装"><a href="#下载-amp-安装" class="headerlink" title="下载 &amp; 安装"></a>下载 &amp; 安装</h2><ul><li><p>下载</p><p><a href="http://39.137.67.79/mirror.bit.edu.cn/apache/zookeeper/zookeeper-3.5.5/apache-zookeeper-3.5.5-bin.tar.gz" target="_blank" rel="noopener">tar包下载</a></p></li><li><p>解压</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> tar zxvf apache-zookeeper-3.5.5-bin.tar.gz -C zookeeper</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>配置</p><p>在 zookeeper 目录下创建目录 data 和 logs 两个目录存储数据和日志</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> mkdir data</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> mkdir logs</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在 conf 目录下新建 zoo.cfg 文件，写入以下内容保存</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tickTime=2000</span><br><span class="line">dataDir=/tools/zookeeper/data</span><br><span class="line">dataLogDir=/tools/zookeeper/logs</span><br><span class="line">clientPort=2181</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>启动 &amp; 停止</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> ./zkServer.sh start</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> ./zkServer.sh stop</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> ./zkServer.sh restart</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> ./zkServer.sh status</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="集群模式"><a href="#集群模式" class="headerlink" title="集群模式"></a>集群模式</h2>]]></content>
    
